videos.description: Lindell Wigginton drives to the basket and finishes with a one handed slam late in the first half for Iowa State.
videos.headline: Wigginton blows by a defender for a wide open slam

videos.description: Cartier Diarra steps back and hits a 3-pointer to tie the game for Kansas State.
videos.headline: Diarra pulls off a James Harden step back to nail 3-pointer

videos.description: Xavier Sneed makes Kansas State's bench go crazy with a huge dunk.
videos.headline: Sneed throws down the one-handed hammer
